Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,宇治抹茶金时吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,宇治抹茶金时？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢惠顾
